sentences: In 1951 he joined the U.S. Marines and played in a military band.
After being discharged in 1953, he moved to San Francisco, where he worked with Earl Hines, Lionel Hampton, and Duke Ellington.
From 1962–1970, he was a member of the Count Basie Orchestra.
He spent the next decade working in television and movies, then returned to Basie's orchestra in 1980 and remained with it until his death in 1984.
